ofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=28&verse=30'>Act 28:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=9&verse=15'>1Co 9:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=2&verse=9'>1Th 2:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=53&chapter=3&verse=8'>2Th 3:8</a><p/><b>(M) UNFAITHFUL MINISTERS,</b> General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=56&verse=10'>Isa 56:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=13'>Jer 6:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=23&verse=11'>Jer 23:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=2&verse=14'>Lam 2:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=33&verse=6'>Eze 33:6</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=3&verse=11'>Mic 3:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=1&verse=15'>Phi 1:15</a><p/><b>(N) FALSE SHEPHERDS,</b> characteristics of<p/><b>Insentiate and Pleasure-loving</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=56&verse=10'>Isa 56:10-12</a><p/><b>Scatter the Flock</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=23&verse=2'>Jer 23:2</a><p/><b>Lead the Sheep astray</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=50&verse=6'>Jer 50:6</a><p/><b>Prey upon the Flock instead of feeding it</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=34&verse=2'>Eze 34:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=34&verse=3'>Eze 34:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=11&verse=17'>Zec 11:17</a><p/><b>Hirelings forsake the Sheep</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=10&verse=12'>Joh 10:12</a><p/><b>(O) FALSE PROPHETS,</b> general references to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=13&verse=5'>Deu 13:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&cha